OL,4,Crescuers one year on
OL,6,FOne year on from being saved from a
OL,7,Froadside near Moffat, six abandoned
OL,8,Fdogs have been reunited with the
OL,9,Fpeople who rescued them.
OL,11,FThe mission to round them up on the
OL,12,FB719 between Moffat and
OL,13,FGreenhillstairs on 9 July 2023 took
OL,14,Fpolice and volunteers hours.
OL,16,FAnimal welfare organisations said the
OL,17,Fdogs were exhausted, terrified,
OL,18,Funderweight and in terrible condition.
OL,20,FFour others were shot that day by a
OL,21,Flocal farmer after they attacked sheep.
