OL,3,CAbandoned dogs reunited with their
OL,4,Crescuers one year on
OL,6,FThe dogs were taken to Dumfries and
OL,7,FGalloway Canine Rescue Centre (DGCRC),
OL,8,Fwhere staff have been rehabilitating
OL,9,Fthem, ready to be re-homed.
OL,11,FMore than #12,000 was raised for the
OL,12,Fdogs at the Dumfries and Galloway
OL,13,Fanimal charity after an appeal last
OL,14,Fsummer.
OL,16,FLee Herron, who has been volunteering
OL,17,Fwith Lost Dogs Dumfries and Galloway
OL,18,Ffor around six years, said: "It took a
OL,19,Flong time to build their trust and
OL,20,Fsecure them that day, it was a real
OL,21,Fchallenge.
