OL,3,CAbandoned dogs reunited with their
OL,4,Crescuers one year on
OL,6,F"It was clear they'd never been
OL,7,Fhandled before or had a collar and
OL,8,Flead on, however, they did really well
OL,9,Fand we were all so relieved when we
OL,10,Fhad them all safe and secure.
OL,12,F"To see how they've improved is
OL,13,Famazing.
OL,15,F"They are so playful and just want to
OL,16,Fhave fun.
OL,18,F"Myself and Roger absolutely loved
OL,19,Fspending time with them one year on
OL,20,Fand we really hope they can find the
OL,21,Fhomes they deserve soon."
