OL,6,FThe dogs, named Toffee, Charlotte,
OL,7,FRae, Meadow, Glen and Brodie, have all
OL,8,Fbeen given names with a Moffat
OL,9,Fconnection linked to streets,
OL,10,Frestaurants and even its famous
OL,11,Fconfectionery.
OL,13,FSergeant Iain Monro and Police
OL,14,FConstable Kelby Kirkpatrick were the
OL,15,Ffirst on scene last year when reports
OL,16,Fcame in about the dogs being abandoned.
OL,18,FSgt Monro said: "It was incredible for
OL,19,Fus to see the dogs and how much
OL,20,Fthey've progressed in the last 12
OL,21,Fmonths.
